{"tid":267680,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Linux] Sudo爆本地端最高權限漏洞","createTime":"2017-06-02T12:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T15:35:27.000Z","uid":80964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b8425f0a02c4117e244541028b2b8ead1f5191","tid":267680,"uid":80964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wl7x4bfc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwl7x4bfc&h=fb307356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果linux系統<span style=\"color: red;\">啟用SELinux</span>，並支援Sudo，擁有Sudo權限的使用者將能利用此一漏洞以<span style=\"color: red;\">任意檔案覆蓋系統</span>，或<span style=\"color: red;\">取得系統的最高權限</span>。<br />\n<br />\n紅帽、SUSE、Debian及Ubuntu等業者已相繼於日前修補自家Linux版本中的Sudo漏洞，該漏洞將允許本地端駭客取得系統的最高權限。<br />\n<br />\n資安業者Qualys在本周二公開揭露了相關漏洞，建立Sudo程式的Todd Miller亦於當天更新了程式。<br />\n<br />\nMiller解釋，假使系統啟用了SELinux（Linux核心安全模組），並支援Sudo，那麼擁有Sudo權限的使用者就能利用該漏洞以任意檔案覆蓋系統，或是取得系統的最高權限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F114635&d=F15XtDPZx7hT4pGQQJPV1dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=59deab7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114635</a><br />\n<br />\n一定係用家問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:用緊Fedora 25"},{"pid":"8021d425708db540eaf1dabb1ceb1c49caed2ee6","tid":267680,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"sudo nano<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}